reviewText: Saw this the first time years ago on Fuse network. Really pretty funny, rap / hip hop stars doing voiceovers on old kung fu movies. Some hilarious stuff in here. I wouldn't pay $10-20 or whatever they were asking at first but for the few bucks they're at now (used), they're well worth it.
I am astonished how quickly I received this item.  Since it is a Christmas present, I do not know how the product quality is but so far extremely pleased.

Finally! Voloume Five and my little man "Break Boy!" is seeing the light of day...now if they would only make that "ill master" action figure into a minimate for me to add to my collection I will be straight...oh yeah, and maybe a "queenie" action figure too, so my man B-Boy can have a shorty to hang out and lamp with.-Grip!
